des:
Mandarmani is a seaside resort village in East Midnapore district of West Bengal, India and at the northern end of the Bay of Bengal. It is a perfect destination for water sports lovers, and in general, adventure-seekers. It is also great for a lazy holiday with family or your spouse. The Mandarmani Beach offers perfect chaos-free vacation, away from the buzzing city life. The beach, not overly crowded like other mainstream beaches, is ideal and totally affordable for your next vacation.
This skill would provide interesting and useful facts about Mandarmani.
